arket because of its large black population before it began the campaign came under fire from religious health and blackinterest groups who expressed concerns about promoting cigarette smoking to blacks on january   reynolds abruptly decided to cancel the cigarette saying that the test marketing would no longer be reliable because of what it called the unfair and biased attention that brand has received facilitiesedit reynolds building entrance in winstonsalem nc the companys headquarters were located in the reynolds building in winstonsalem for more than fifty years built in  the story building was designed by the same architects shreve  lamb who later designed the empire state building in new york city built in  at a cost of  million  million in  dollars the whitaker park plant had  square feet of manufacturing space and was considered the worlds largest and most modern cigarettemanufacturing plant it was announced in may  that cigarette manufacturing would cease at whitaker park by mid this had been done manufacturing formerly performed at the whitaker park plant was consolidated in the moremodern tobaccoville plant on january   reynolds announced that whitaker park was being donated to whitaker park development authority inc started in april  by winstonsalem business inc the winstonsalem alliance and wake forest university in september  rj reynolds industries moved the first of  headquarters employees into the notyetcompleted  million squarefoot glass and steel world headquarters building being built across reynolds boulevard from the whitaker park plant at the same time the company had plans for a new skyscraper downtown the current headquarters the rjr plaza building is  stories tall and was completed in  adjacent to the original  reynolds building the tobacco company moved its headquarters to rjr plaza in  and the  building continued to be used for some company offices until  the older building stood vacant until new owners in  began the process to convert it